parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front wheel bearings can cause the motorcycle to lose control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the coolant pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, stalling, or failure, which can result in accidents or leave the rider stranded.
